---
title: Southeast Asian Pork & Sesame Dressing with Basmati Rice & Pickled Cucumber
description: Whip up a tasty bowl of Asian-spiced pork strips tossed with colourful veggies and an easy sesame sauce packed with umami flavours. With added crunch from the pickled cucumber and crushed peanuts, what's not to love?
